00:27:27.900 --> 00:27:29.000
I believe that.

00:27:29.000 --> 00:27:29.640
CARMEN MARIA MACHADO: Oh, yeah.

00:27:29.640 --> 00:27:30.450
AUDIENCE: Yes, I know.

00:27:30.450 --> 00:27:31.830
CARMEN MARIA MACHADO: I'm going
