00:28:33.430 --> 00:28:35.170
sort of getting like, OK,
that's a writer that I like.

00:28:35.170 --> 00:28:36.628
Here's stuff they're
interested in,

00:28:36.628 --> 00:28:38.280
books that are
important to them.

00:28:38.280 --> 00:28:40.750
It's a really cool way to
sort of get, a, as a writer,

00:28:40.750 --> 00:28:44.867
amping other writers' voices,
and also helping your readers

00:28:44.867 --> 00:28:47.200
learn about other books that
they should be checking out

00:28:47.200 --> 00:28:50.000
that you like.

00:28:50.000 --> 00:28:53.355
