very simple sort of pleasure

00:30:39.284 --> 00:30:41.450
thinking a lot about like
the choices that have been

00:30:41.450 --> 00:30:43.040
made at every level, right?

00:30:43.040 --> 00:30:45.170
And who gets published
is a political decision.

00:30:45.170 --> 00:30:46.130
Whose work gets
published and who's

00:30:46.130 --> 00:30:47.713
work doesn't get
published, whose work

00:30:47.713 --> 00:30:49.130
gets amplified in certain ways.

00:30:49.130 --> 00:30:51.755
Who the characters are.

00:30:51.755 --> 00:30:53.630
Who is allowed to tell
what kinds of stories.

00:30:57.100 --> 00:30:59.540
These are all really
inherently, really fraught

00:30:59.540 --> 00:31:00.410
political positions.

00:31:00.410 --> 00:31:03.290
And the idea that you can just
write, make a piece of art

00:31:03.290 --> 00:31:05.390
or make a story that is
not political-- to me,

00:31:05.390 --> 00:31:07.300
it's just utter
folly and reveals

00:31:07.300 --> 00:31:10.400
a deep sort of misunderstanding
of what art is.

00:31:13.320 --> 00:31:14.830
Yeah, sorry.

